{"tid":44474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"換鈔新政後　印度拐賣兒童情況有改善","createTime":"2016-12-18T10:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T09:20:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c33385198292416a1f85b31c6fcf05aa3080109a","tid":44474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161218/photo/bknint-20161218051629369-1218_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161218%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161218051629369-1218_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=96ec58cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Z5TS2SyY0ErunK%2BbJR7OEwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2d91229a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 印度總理莫迪於上月宣布換鈔新政，圖以廢除舊版大面額紙幣的政策，以打擊貪腐、洗黑錢和假銀紙等罪行，引發國民爭議。有兒童保護組織近日發現，印度推行新政後，拐賣兒童的現像有下降的趨勢。 <br />\n<br />\n關注童工問題的孟買慈善機構布拉罕（Pratham）成員巴泰德（Sugandha Patade）日前指，一些來自北方邦、比哈爾邦和拉賈斯坦邦的童工，會到孟買東部工作，但在上個月，未有發現新的童工到當地工作，而本來在那裏工作的童工，已經被送走。 <br />\n<br />\n孟買警方則表示，換鈔新政或打擊拐賣兒童的犯罪組織，但現在要確認童工和兒童拐賣現像下降，與新政策有關，還是言之尚早。 <br />\n<br />\n印度童工權益分子兼2014諾貝爾和平獎得主薩蒂亞爾蒂（Kailash Satyarthi）指，近日已不再常見人口販子在印度地區運送兒童，因為他們不能用黑錢來支持他們的非法活動，販賣人口不像以往般容易。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161218/bknint-20161218051629369-1218_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161218%2Fbknint-20161218051629369-1218_17011_001.html&d=Z5TS2SyY0ErunK%2BbJR7OEwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=42588f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161218/bknint-20161218051629369-1218_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"542dd211b77a163e44ab462e0ee09e0abc39583e","tid":44474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3ad135b2925a29574b0d287c473d2d952429c7","tid":44474,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:26:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲都係短期效果<br />\n遲早搵到方法<br />\n有心就趁依家打殘班仆街"},{"pid":"b0b033933b65bb9397605fc0439097932729dad4","tid":44474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb274d4ec2cf59305d5c818d949b3d201e7c74d2","tid":44474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f50c4473072e7912d0bf30ee2fc27a7e01705e","tid":44474,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"咁咪摧毀經濟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ca2aafeb50274030bdcd2f79c9dbd2ee6f134b","tid":44474,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"Money laundering 有好多方法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}